contracts/visibility.sol.content:
/*

private -> functions and state variables declared as internal can only be accessed
            inside the contract in which they are declared

internal -> functions and state variables declared as internal can be accessed by a 
            by a contract and its child contract

public -> function and state variables declared as public can be accessed by anyone

external -> functions and state variables declared as extefrnal can only be accessed
            from outside the contract and not from inside
*/
